---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | AC Plumbers"
  description="Read AC Plumbers' Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal data. Your privacy is our priority."
  keywords="privacy policy, data protection, AC Plumbers, Brighton, personal data"
>
  <section class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-primary-600">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: [Insert Date]</p>

    <p>
      At AC Plumb, we are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your
      data in a transparent and secure way.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      AC Plumb is a plumbing and heating company based in Brighton, UK, serving
      areas such as Hove, Lewes, Worthing, and nearby towns.
    </p>

    <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Contact details (e.g., name, email, phone number)</li>
      <li>Technical data (e.g., IP address, browser type)</li>
      <li>Usage data (pages visited, time on site)</li>
      <li>Information submitted via forms</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Why We Collect Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to enquiries or service requests</li>
      <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
      <li>Send service-related communications</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Lawful Basis</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Consent (e.g., contact forms)</li>
      <li>Contract (e.g., when providing quotes)</li>
      <li>Legitimate interest (e.g., analytics)</li>
      <li>Legal compliance (e.g., safety checks)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Sharing Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Service providers (hosting, analytics)</li>
      <li>Legal authorities (if required by law)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We never sell your data.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Access, correct or delete your data</li>
      <li>Object or restrict processing</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      <li>Lodge a complaint with the ICO</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. How We Protect Your Data</h2>
    <p>We use secure servers, encryption, and strict access control.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      AC Plumb<br />
      [Insert Address]<br />
      Email: [Insert Email]<br />
      Phone: [Insert Number]
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
